Formed in Th-Target by Bombardment with 0.15-24 GeV.
Last checking has been done.
DATE is corrected
The Targets stacks consisted of 44 mg/**2 Gold foil,
sandwiched between one pair of 20 mg/cm**2 Aluminum
foils, which collected the Recoil Ions in the forward
and backward directions. The different target stacks
were separated from each other by guard foil. Several
Aluminum foils were added at different locations in the
stack to serve as beam monitors.
